<span><span STYLE="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:">[53]</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></SPAN></A>
<span STYLE="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:">陈寅恪先生右眼失明的时间很早，左目失明是在</SPAN><span>1944</SPAN><span STYLE="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:">年底，时在四川成都，任教燕京大学。《雨僧日记》</SPAN><span>1944</SPAN><span STYLE="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:">年</SPAN><span>12</SPAN><span STYLE="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:">月</SPAN><span>12</SPAN><span STYLE="font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:">日</SPAN><span STYLE="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:">载：“访寅恪于广益学舍宅，始知寅恪左目今晨又不明”。三联书店版《雨僧日记》第九册，</SPAN><span>1999</SPAN><span STYLE="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:">年，第</SPAN><span>374</SPAN><span STYLE="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:">页。同年</SPAN><span>12</SPAN><span STYLE="font-family: 宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:">月</SPAN><span>18</SPAN><span STYLE="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:">日遵医嘱手术，但效果不佳，实际上已失明。</SPAN></P>
